---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Zeeshan Haider" lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <Navbar currentLang="en" />

  <main class="min-h-screen pt-24 px-6 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 reveal">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-4">
          Privacy <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent to-accent2">Policy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-muted text-lg">Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none text-muted reveal">
        <p>At <strong>zxsprd.com</strong>, accessible from https://zxsprd.com, your privacy is of utmost importance to me. As an IT and Security Engineer, I practice what I preach: your data is handled with the highest level of care and security.</p>

        <h2>1. Information Collection and Use</h2>
        <p>I do not use invasive tracking cookies or third-party analytics that compromise your privacy. The only personal information I collect is voluntarily provided by you through the <strong>Contact Form</strong> (Name, Email, Subject, and Message). This data is securely processed via Netlify Forms and is used solely to reply to your inquiry.</p>

        <h2>2. Contact Form Data</h2>
        <p>When you submit a message via the contact form, the data is transmitted securely. I will never sell, rent, or share your personal information with any third parties. Your data is kept only as long as necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it was provided.</p>

        <h2>3. External Links</h2>
        <p>This website contains links to external sites (such as my LinkedIn, GitHub, or old portfolio links). Please be aware that I am not responsible for the privacy practices of these other sites. I encourage you to read the privacy statements of any external website you visit.</p>

        <h2>4. Security</h2>
        <p>This website is hosted on Netlify and built using modern, secure static site generation (Astro). Because the site is mostly static HTML, the attack surface is minimal. I implement industry-standard security practices to protect against unauthorized access.</p>

        <h2>5. Your Consent</h2>
        <p>By using my website, you consent to this privacy policy. If I update this policy, the changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

        <h2>6. Contact Me</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact me at: <a href="mailto:zeeshan.haider28@gmail.com">zeeshan.haider28@gmail.com</a></p>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>